---
title: Herby Seared Steak & Veggie Fries with Onion Chutney Sauce
description: A delicious beef steak can win over many hearts and we believe this herby garlic steak will make yours flutter. If that’s not enough
though, maybe try one of the veggie fries. To really seal the deal, top the steak with a sweet onion chutney sauce.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 30g carbohydrates per serving.*
